===Etymology 1===
{{IPAfont|⟨to<sub>2</sub>ma⟩}} → *{{IPAchar|/təma/}} → {{IPAchar|/toma/}}

Likely from {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=とま|-}}.

Possibly derived from the verb {{ja-r|泊まる|とまる|to stay}}, or from {{ja-r|止まる|とまる|to stop}}, in reference to thatched roofs under which boats or people stay, or which stop falling rain. Other suggested sources include {{ja-r|鳥羽|とは|bird's wing; feather}} or {{ja-compound|戸|と|衣|も|t1=door; house|t2=clothing; covering}}.<ref>{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>

